{"name":"Brazier of Holy Fire","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"craftsmanship":"common","description":"<p>A versatile weapon in the hands of a skilled user, the Brazier of Holy Fire works as a devastating melee weapon, an inspirational icon, and, in times of need, a deadly flamethrower to incinerate heretics and witches. Any character who can draw line of sight to an ally wielding an active Brazier of Holy Fire gains a +10 bonus to his Willpower tests. Additionally, it can be used as a heavy flamer with a clip size of 1. Once fired, it loses the Flame quality in melee until it is reloaded, a process that takes roughly 20 minutes and involves several special hymns.</p>","availability":"very-rare","weight":6,"class":"melee","type":"","range":0,"rateOfFire":{"single":0,"burst":0,"full":0},"damage":"1d10+5","damageType":"energy","penetration":"3","clip":{"max":0,"value":0},"reload":"","special":"Flame, Unbalanced","attack":0},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_Resources/icons/Meele/flaming-trident.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Q1OLaFj6RjgjZyqv"}
{"name":"Fire Gauntlets","permission":{"default":0,"Q8i5xjnghNCdqNHG":3},"type":"weapon","data":{"craftsmanship":"common","description":"<p>More commonly known as Judgement&rsquo;s Grasp or the Hands of the Emperor, Magnus-Pattern Fire Gauntlets are a peculiar matching set of metallic gloves linked to small forearm-mounted promethium chambers. By extending his fingers, a priest can safely coat his hands in a nimbus of fire, awing gathered crowds and frightening mutants. As a Free Action, the user can ignite the gauntlets, granting a +20 bonus to Intimidate tests. They always come in pairs, and the reservoir lasts until the end of the encounter (or 2d10 minutes outside of structured time).</p>","availability":"very-rare","weight":1,"class":"melee","type":"","range":0,"rateOfFire":{"single":0,"burst":0,"full":0},"damage":"1d10","damageType":"impact","penetration":"2","clip":{"max":0,"value":0},"reload":"","special":"Flame, Unbalanced","attack":0},"flags":{},"img":"modules/dh2e_Resources/icons/Meele/flaming-trident.svg","effects":[],"_id":"SxSFoMRZ3ouJtxyv"}
